			<p>Metal Craft Al-Ain is dedicated to providing information and resources for youngsters interested in the metal and steel industry. Metals and steel are essential materials used in various industries, including construction, manufacturing, and transportation.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Metals: Metals are naturally occurring elements that are typically hard, shiny, and good conductors of electricity. Examples of metals include iron, copper, and aluminum.</li>
				<li>Steel: Steel is an alloy of iron and carbon, known for its strength, durability, and versatility. It is widely used in construction, transportation, and consumer goods.</li>
